   The 2020 Paris Motor Show, a multi-event festival
   From October 1st - 11th

   Beyond the Porte de Versailles, a truly central location, Paris will
   become the setting for this 2020 edition thanks to several events
   packed with content:

     * Porte de Versailles: The PARIS MOTOR SHOW
       At the Porte de Versailles Parc des Expositions, the Motor Show
       will host Automotive and Motorbike exhibitions, offering its
       visitors denser content and new events for an optimal visit
       experience.
     * MOVIN’ON PARIS 2020:
       In the specific context of the 2020 Motor Show, Movin’On will rely
       on its experience and its unique network of partners in the field
       of sustainable mobility to encourage discussions and bring together
       initiatives by the major players and professionals of the sector,
       in order to support the development of automotive mobility while
       reducing its environmental impact.
     * The expanded Motor Show:
       At the Porte de Versailles and other sites, this 2020 edition will
       go in search of communities of automotive, motorbike and mobility
       enthusiasts and professionals, by offering them exciting side
       events.

   The 2020 edition will accentuate the transformation begun in 2018. It
   adopts the programming logic of a festival. Each participant will have
   the opportunity to build a personalized journey via an innovative
   mobile application.

   o know all about the 2020 edition, subscribe to our newsletter !

